    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎来到《Sky Fields》</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以无人机的视角探索《Sky Fields》，在漂浮的岛屿间冒险，并扩展你的史莱姆们收藏。穿越充满各种Slime种类的独特环境，进行战斗，收集资源和原始黏液，以孵化和孵化新的Slimes。每种Slime类型都有独特的外观、强度和稀有度！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >特点：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >滑翔进入《Sky Fields》的世界，穿越独特的岛屿和生物群落。但要小心——暴君军团潜伏在荒芜之地！你能挺身而出对抗他们吗？探索坚固的避难所，征服危险的岛屿，并在旅途中收集珍贵资源。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325480/extras/81fbf203d01316b009fad86129af8129.poster.avif?t=1760632885\" width=615 height=183 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325480/extras/81fbf203d01316b009fad86129af8129.webm?t=1760632885\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战斗与升级</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在回合制战斗中策略性地安排你的攻击。尝试不同的队伍组合，利用史莱姆们之间的协同效果。将辅助和施法者放在近战单位后方，打造理想的阵型。挑战强大敌人，并通过升级提升你的队伍实力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325480/extras/dfb8c1e70e7954dcdf2d6ffbee708910.poster.avif?t=1760632885\" width=615 height=183 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325480/extras/dfb8c1e70e7954dcdf2d6ffbee708910.webm?t=1760632885\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >创建你的史莱姆！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >融合你的生物，传承能力、属性，甚至是独特的外观。通过深度的繁殖系统，提供无尽的可能性，你可以打造终极史莱姆队伍！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325480/extras/dbad35b1e0af2b8431ad0cdd5153fe88.poster.avif?t=1760632885\" width=615 height=183 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325480/extras/dbad35b1e0af2b8431ad0cdd5153fe88.webm?t=1760632885\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >商人</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >留意定期出现的流动商人。用你的资源兑换金币，并用金币购买宝箱，可能解锁超稀有的史莱姆。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325480/extras/7f51ac22060e310191683c2e358a7c98.poster.avif?t=1760632885\" width=615 height=183 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325480/extras/7f51ac22060e310191683c2e358a7c98.webm?t=1760632885\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
